00:02:11.340 --> 00:02:12.930
We are in the corporate world.

00:02:12.930 --> 00:02:15.960
You know, that
wouldn't play out here.

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:20.040
Even if I was slightly
concerned about what

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:24.760
my boss might say if I did
or didn't do something,

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:27.030
nobody's going to die.

00:02:27.030 --> 00:02:32.790
I'm not going to kill 96 people
if I make a wrong decision.

00:02:32.790 --> 00:02:37.610
Well, maybe we'll come
